  "instructions": "1. Place the water, molasses, vegetable oil, and salt in the pan of the bread machine in the order recommended by the manufacturer.\n\n2. Add the all-purpose flour, rye flour, brown sugar, cocoa powder, caraway seed, and bread machine yeast on top of the wet ingredients.\n\n3. Select the Basic cycle, and press Start to begin the bread-making process.\n\n4. Once your bread is cooked, let it cool and then slice to serve.",
